Sandbox tab: replay history, save/export runs; Signals status pills; journal export/import

- scripts/update_chameleon.py + update_catchup.py now emit rolling 250-day
  signal_history.json with date, signal, price, regime/momenta per strategy
- standalone/trade.html: new Sandbox tab replays history as if you had traded
  the signals (one strategy or "Both must agree"), with equity curve SVG,
  stats, trade table, and Save/Export/Import runs (JSON + CSV) so runs can
  be stored in iPad Files / Google Drive, not just the browser
- Signals header now has auto pills: Data age, Live gap (Frankfurter vs
  bundle), Readiness 0-5 score
- Journal: Export JSON / Export CSV / Import JSON buttons
- Fix switchStrategy to take explicit element (no global event)
- Replace misleading 5-min JSON reload with a single init load + manual refresh
- Sync standalone/index.html
- docs/USER_GUIDE.md: document Sandbox, pills, journal export
